<h3 class="date"><a href="/2007/feb/19/">&#x27a0;</a> February 19, 2007</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    <div class="flickrentry entry">
        <h4>On the Poop Deck</h4>

        <a href="http://flickr.com/photos/groovymother/395898089/"><img class="flickrphoto" alt="On the Poop Deck" src="http://farm1.static.flickr.com/154/395898089_cb0aa56a12_m.jpg" height="240" width="180" /></a>

        <p>
            <p>Raking through some old photos, I found this one from when Joy &amp; I took an Alaskan cruise in September 2002.</p>

<p>I brought along a fake plastic dog turd from Boston (which originally was sent to me from Scotland by my mum as part of my Christmas presents one year) *just* to take this photo of the &quot;poop deck&quot;.</p>
        </p>

