    <div class="flickrentry entry">
        <h4>Gardening of a Saturday Afternoon</h4>

        <a href="http://flickr.com/photos/groovymother/250729421/"><img class="flickrphoto" alt="Gardening of a Saturday Afternoon" src="http://farm1.static.flickr.com/118/250729421_ffbaeb40b6_m.jpg" height="180" width="240" /></a>

